data.description: Move in ready home situated on four spacious lots with three bedrooms, eat in kitchen and dining room area.  This home does has a first floor bedroom and bathroom and the other two bedrooms are located upstairs with GIANT  walk in closets! There is a small room between the two bedrooms currently being used as an extra walk in closet and would make a great nursery or home office!  This yard is VERY spacious and home also has a nice one car garage!  New Septic installed in 2022!!
